               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-41-person319">
                  THOMAS 
                  MOORE
               <interp inst="t18180401-41-person319" type="surname" value="MOORE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180401-41-person319" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180401-41-person319" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Littlefield, who is a <rs id="t18180401-41-viclabel237" type="occupation">carrier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-41-victim318 t18180401-41-viclabel237"></join>. I brought a box of linen from Shepperton to town, and delivered it to the prisoner to take to Hatton-garden. I gave it out of my cart to him in <placeName id="t18180401-41-crimeloc238">Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-41-crimeloc238" type="placeName" value="Fleet-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-41-crimeloc238" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-41-off235 t18180401-41-crimeloc238"></join> - I knew him before.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. ALLEY. Q. Did you not lose it out of the waggon - A. No, I am positive of it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-41-person320">
                  MARY 
                  PERRYMAN
               <interp inst="t18180401-41-person320" type="surname" value="PERRYMAN"></interp>
