                  </persName>
            . I live at Shepperton. I delivered the box to Moore, to take to No. 99, Hatton-garden-it contained the articles stated in the indictment.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-41-person321">
                  THOMAS 
                  POND
               <interp inst="t18180401-41-person321" type="surname" value="POND"></interp>
