                     <interp inst="t18180401-41-person321" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was a passenger in the waggon - I saw the box at the tail of the cart. I helped it on a man's shoulder, to take it to Hatton-garden. I should not know him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-41-person322">
